Cross-over actress Toyin Abraham has become counselor, going by the several messages she has been receiving from fans, who believe she can give advice on different issues. Having dwelled on some negative acts in the past which the actress/producer revealed had affected her career, she has since become a role model that most youths have developed respect and deep feeling for, espacially with some of her successful movies at the box office recently. The actress has developed a platform where it is easy for her followers to speak about their personal issues and getting advice from other followers without being criticized. Toyin recently had some issues with fellow actress Mercy Aigbe. Though she later apologized to Mercy, this made some people to link the disput to a publicity stuntfor her newly released movie, ‘The Ghost and the Tout.’